5. Chess RL — REINFORCE Policy Gradient Agent
The most complex program in CJC-Lang’s test suite. A complete reinforcement learning system: a chess environment with legal move generation, check detection, and game termination; a policy network MLP; softmax action selection via categorical sampling; and REINFORCE gradient updates with manual backpropagation through the policy.
